normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁要睇返其他出幾多</blockquote><br />\n咁就唔關咩市道唔好啦大哥<br />\n<br />\n鳩up冇譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n出面出得低咪市道唔好囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 補習係有好大demand 不過唔代表大過supply<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"385d569d0f5115b911d52099b0b811856b5f25b0","tid":426613,"uid":131208,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T07:14:21.000Z","msg":"而家做緊IB補習社<br />\n一日返4,5個鐘，但返7日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平均人工都係多4,5千<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a974559f23c1c30f077af660fa25a8da87e4d24f","tid":426613,"uid":70021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T17:24:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>假如之後間補習社做大咗， 會唔會有機會加底薪?好有興趣入同長做， 不過唔想一世14k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n到你做大左就唔係睇底薪，而係睇bonus架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f2638d9d8c525ec5eefd0c905dcfb77f6661a80","tid":426613,"uid":70021,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T17:27:17.000Z","msg":"上面好多巴打話低人工<br />\n你地可以上jobsDB睇下出面請緊幾錢<br />\n我唔敢講我老細出得高，但應該係合理市價<br />\n仲要講緊我地係有bonus <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n每月學費收入高過某個數就有得分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29df366374ab68a505b8e35404c1c130c649c0f5","tid":426613,"uid":131836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T17:39:30.000Z","msg":"我開35k<br />\n唔做admin野，淨教<br />\n5天工作，每日最多兩堂<br />\n唔好叫我send cv<br />\n叫你老細直接搵我傾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978c55bfb2ebbff4bb8644fcbee060e56a3028af","tid":426613,"uid":10034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T17:46:38.000Z","msg":"如果一月先返到工考唔考慮？"},{"pid":"a2b991a145e85ec8e4c1c18c0fc55e872957bef5","tid":426613,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:38:49.000Z","msg":"醒少少既返1V1私補, 一星期返2日都唔止呢個數"},{"pid":"270897e9b2d7f7da5e387066de0d2e4198c59da6","tid":426613,"uid":26287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:19:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>代老細Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  要屌send email過去屌佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小型補習社  招聘全職補習導師<br />\n教DSE專科班<br />\n5天工作，星期六或日有機會返工(閒日放返)<br />\n要教書日子返1pm-9pm (各位巴絲唔好屌，補習社係返呢個時間架...)<br />\n唔洗教書日子返9am-5pm (整下筆記，做下網上宣傳)<br />\n油尖旺區返工<br />\n14k底  過左某個學生人數會有bonus分<br />\n歡迎Freshgrad<br />\n希望請長工<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔係玩玩下果d，所以最好有興趣長遠響呢行發展先好apply<br />\n不過你想騎牛搵馬老細又請左你既，我吹你唔漲既....<br />\n<br />\n最好 DSE 5* / AL B 以上  或者  大學本科讀相關學科<br />\n<br />\n有興趣send CV過去 Tutor.Recruitment001@gmail.com</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9938c8ebcec8b7639d51e7db7593ff3e1bbed4","tid":426613,"uid":63418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T04:50:56.000Z","msg":"14k <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己做私補都分分鐘高人工過佢"},{"pid":"6590c6f770816dbd7a3a0a1f5d7751da92f43dd1","tid":426613,"uid":43117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:38:13.000Z","msg":"DSE 5* / AL B 以上<br />\n<br />\n就唔會同你返14K啦"},{"pid":"5645f7c105f33413930d295dea5d34167286b138","tid":426613,"uid":34222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T06:04:01.000Z","msg":"讀緊u 私補都搵到啦<br />\n<br />\n仲冇你返咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ba964a9ab193153d11a40287800de7